Common.LocationDescription.Common.Text: The Liberty Square towers are conveniently located at the entrance to Greenville’s CBD within walking distance to over 100 restaurants, retail and local attractions.

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
- Building signage opportunities
- The buildings are canvased with windows providing tons of natural light
- On-site restaurants included JAC's and The Commerce Club
- Parking available in adjacent city garages
- Building security 24/7
- State-of-the-art Fitness Center
- Outdoor courtyard with WiFi and speakers
Downtown Class A Office Building inclusive of a private, attached parking garage.

Common.LocationDescription.Common.Text:
The building is located near the White Horse Road interchange off I-85
(100,400 VPD).

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
50 Datastream Plaza presents a unique offering in the market given the availability
of surface parking and prime signage opportunity with over 500 feet of interstate
frontage.
